						 <p>It wasn't intended to be a pun, but that works. I'm glad you 'get it'. It wasn't supposed to be a riddle and I tried to run it by chat a few times to make sure it makes sense. It's a portal connecting your head to an old man's hammer. That's it.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">There&nbsp;is&nbsp;one&nbsp;hidden&nbsp;thing.</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>The D-Class is the same one from SCP-1616. Gotta save money yall.</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
